{"tid":887234,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Facebook已引入OCR功能，言論恐進一步受制","createTime":"2018-11-02T17:22:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T03:51:57.000Z","uid":34035,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"16b6270f2ad0e14e54c0b30130de33f09c331cd0","tid":887234,"uid":34035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:22:26.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇火星到，我最近發現FB多了OCR (optical character recognition) 功能，<br />\nAI會自動掃描上傳到FB server 既所有圖片，不論有否公開。<br />\n想測試既話，可以嘗試用任一帳號上傳包含了正常字體的英文文字的圖片<br />\n(手寫、經設計後等OCR讀唔到既特殊字形無效)<br />\n目前好似只有英文可以辯認，但相信不久會延伸到其他語系 (例如中文)<br />\nFB旗下既IG好似都有 (我冇用IG所以冇test)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.zdnet.com/article/facebook-pumps-up-character-recognition-to-mine-memes/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zdnet.com%2Farticle%2Ffacebook-pumps-up-character-recognition-to-mine-memes%2F&d=iHEvM3WJGHg6PeUwLvKyrdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=9ca62311\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.zdnet.com/article/facebook-pumps-up-character-recognition-to-mine-memes/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://code.fb.com/ai-research/rosetta-understanding-text-in-images-and-videos-with-machine-learning/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcode.fb.com%2Fai-research%2Frosetta-understanding-text-in-images-and-videos-with-machine-learning%2F&d=iHEvM3WJGHg6PeUwLvKyrdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=4961e360\" target=\"_blank\">https://code.fb.com/ai-research/rosetta-understanding-text-in-images-and-videos-with-machine-learning/</a><br />\n我所搵到既相關資料，最早係9月初，但好似至今完全沒有人提及<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以後可能hate speech、種族歧視(that N word)、政治異見，轉成圖片都會被bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁同百度、微博有撚分別？想轉用其他SNS，但朋友又冇人轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://code.fb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/CodeBlog_penguinG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcode.fb.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2FCodeBlog_penguinG.png&h=4fe2b7a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33a9bed79cf3e379d502db1eb686397075d97a4f","tid":887234,"uid":34035,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/03/013735_d192713da13826fe29bb34068e9cd95a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F03%2F013735_d192713da13826fe29bb34068e9cd95a.jpg&h=2d7db1db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁都讀到"},{"pid":"92b5d90a15a6a2436eaecb1a97dfe523ad654eda","tid":887234,"uid":196924,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"33a9bed79cf3e379d502db1eb686397075d97a4f","tid":887234,"uid":34035,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/03/013735_d192713da13826fe29bb34068e9cd95a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F03%2F013735_d192713da13826fe29bb34068e9cd95a.jpg&h=2d7db1db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁都讀到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:59:09.000Z","msg":"咁都讀唔到就唔叫OCR啦大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5139653440cfe25807f07a9be4447e25087e99c3","tid":887234,"uid":28563,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T18:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://drop.wtako.net/file/b5dc19a2018eb4eca382a6a2dece796665e3c29e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrop.wtako.net%2Ffile%2Fb5dc19a2018eb4eca382a6a2dece796665e3c29e.png&h=20f987a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6152451294f74db07fde24ef2c9e22d85cf0e66","tid":887234,"uid":63452,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T18:27:22.000Z","msg":"政見就話唔應該bam，但係hate speech 同racism 嘢都唔俾bam? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9ede5452591748a58499